System Shock 2 is one of the greatest FPS games in all times, and have been nominated GOTY by several magazines. For those who have not yet enyoyed this fine game or have lost it long gone - here it is!&lt;p&gt;

You can play as a all out brute assaulter,
a clevir hacker bypassing security
or a flashy cool &quot;OSA&quot; with psionic abilitys (telekinetics, pyrokinetics etc).&lt;p&gt;

