Minimum Requirements: 200MHz - 32mb ram&lt;p&gt;

Im not realy shure what &quot;virgin image&quot; is supposed to be, but this download is not a image. It is a cracked compilation of SS2 with patches applied allowing co-op and WinXP support. Dont like it, dont download it - Simple.&lt;p&gt;


